posting_body: ['13560 Technology Dr #1221 Eden Prairie, Minnesota 55344', 'Price: $1350.00', 'Deposit: $1350.00', 'High demand Southwest Station 1 bed, 1 bath condo in the heart of Eden Prairie.', 'This unit comes with 1 assigned underground heated garage space as well as a storage locker.', 'You’ll love the open layout provided by the peninsula kitchen, built in office space and cozy nook added by the balcony.', 'In unit full size laundry plus additional in unit storage.', 'Spacious bedroom with walk-in closet and comfort height bath vanity.', 'Unit is located in the same building as all amenities such as: indoor basketball court, fitness center, sauna & more!', 'Available October 9th-1 yr lease.', 'Tenant pays gas & electric & onetime move in/out fee of $100.', '1 pet allowed (no puppies) w/$25/mo pet rent.', 'Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Application Fee: $45/ adult non-refundable.', 'Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Renters insurance required.', 'Section 8 not approved.', 'Minimum 24 hour notice to show.', 'Pet Policy: 1 pet allowed (no puppies) w/$25/mo pet rent.', 'Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Property Features', 'Condo', '1 bed', '1 bath', 'Built 2003', '1 Parking Spaces', 'Land is 794 square', 'Floor Area is 794 square', 'Garage', 'Balcony', 'Ducted Heating', 'Ducted Cooling', 'Amusement Room', 'Attached Garage', 'Balcony', 'Club House', 'deck', 'Hennepin County', 'Sauna', 'School District 272', 'Visit our website at <URL> for more information.']
